title: Tremors 2 - Aftershocks (1996) (Fred Ward, Michael Gross)
description:
TREMORS 2 - AFTERSHOCKS - 1996

  When a remote Mexican oilfield comes down with a nasty case of Graboids (for the uninitiated: giant carnivorous worms with tunneling abilities that put Bugs Bunny to shame), it's up to those veteran monster exterminators Burt and Earl (Michael Gross and the wonderful Fred Ward, reprising their roles from the first film) to save the day--and accumulate some much-needed payola in the process. But this time, the slimy critters may have a few new tricks up their...um, sleeves.

  Starring: Fred Ward, Helen Shaver, Christopher Gartin, Michael Gross, Marco Hernandez.

  Directed by: S.S. Wilson.

  Quality: Very Good Xvid from DVD.

  Length: 1hr. 39min.

  Language: English.

  Size: 688 x 432
